{"pin":"BB00147","subcodes":[{"code":"BB00147","anchor":"","title":"Du’a’i yawmi nisfi sha’ban","first_line":"Glorified art Thou, O my God! I and all things bear witness that verily Thou art God, and that there is none other God but Thee, alone, without peer. Thine is the creation and the command; Thou givest life and causeth death, and verily Thou art the Ever-Living Who dieth not. Within Thy grasp is the dominion of all things; Thou createst what Thou willest [3.5s]... ...Glory be unto Thee, O Lord! Although Thou mayest cause a person to be destitute of all earthly possessions… O Lord! Provide for the speedy growth of the Tree of Thy divine Unity… Ordain for me, O my Lord, and for those who believe in Thee","first_line_orig":"بسم الله الامنع الاقدس. سبحانک اللهم لاشهدنک و کل شیء علی انک انت الله لا اله الا انت وحدک لا شریک لک لک الخلق و الامر یحی و یمیت و انک انت الحی لا یموت فی قبضبتک ملکوت کل شیء یبدع ما یشاء  ","language":"1","word_count":"1300","subjects":"@prayer for martyrs, @justice and wrath of God, @Manifestation of God as tree of life; sadratu'l-muntaha, @chastisement and requital, @power and sovereignty of God; omnipotence of God","translations":[{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"},{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"zh-Hans","lang_name":"Simplified Chinese"},{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"lo","lang_name":"Lao"}]},{"code":"BB00147GRO","anchor":"gro","translations":[{"language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"de","lang